divs: Sighting DetailsI walked my kids to the bus stop this morning and took several pictures along the way. I got home and downloaded them right after and noticed 2 pictures with something odd in the back ground. I zoomed in and noticed a V shaped UFO and a Triangle shaped UFO off in the distance. I never saw this when I took the pictures. I think they are very clear and would like to know what you think. Taken at 8 in the morning. I will send them in order. 1,2,3 The way I took them. First picture has nothing. Just to show you.
Summary: Did not discover till I downloaded my pictures.
